---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import BackToTopButton from "../components/BackToTop.astro";
---

<Layout title="Interesting Stuffs">
  <div class="container standard-dialog p-4 mr-4">
    <div class="header">
      <p class="heading">Interesting Stuffs</p>
      <h1 style="text-align: center">Try find something you like ;)</h1>
      <p style="text-align: right">Btw I � Unicode</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="content-item css">
        <h3>Cool Style Sheets</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href="https://sakofchit.github.io/system.css">system.css</a>
            <p>I love this soooo much, that I decide use this decorate my blog.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/jdan/98.css">98.css</a>
            <p>I would use this to make some dialog.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/khang-nd/7.css">7.css</a>
            <p>Windows 7 style css, why there still have people using 7?</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item etc">
        <h3>Something else</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.mindprod.com/jgloss/unmain.html">Unmaintainable code</a>
            <p>Feels like enterprise jvav guide.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://testing.googleblog.com/2008/07/how-to-write-3v1l-untestable-code.html">Untestable code</a>
            <p>Who use unit test, aha?</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://alwaysjudgeabookbyitscover.com/">Always judge a book by it's cover</a>
            <p></p>
          </li>
          <img src="/images/stuffs/bookcover.jpg" style="max-width: 200px" />👈 Example
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item rice">
        <h3>Rice</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <details class="gnome">
              <summary>gnome</summary>
              <img src="/images/rices/gnome/rice4.png" style="max-width: 90%" />
              <img src="/images/rices/gnome/rice5.png" style="max-width: 90%" />
              <img src="/images/rices/gnome/rice6.png" style="max-width: 90%" />
              <br />
            </details>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <details class="win">
              <summary>windows 11</summary>
              <img src="/images/rices/windows/rice.png" style="max-width: 90%" />
              <br />
            </details>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <details class="kde">
              <summary>KDE Plasma</summary>
              <img src="/images/rices/kde/rice.png" style="max-width: 90%" />
              <br /><img src="/images/rices/kde/rice1.png" style="max-width: 90%" />
              <br /><img src="/images/rices/kde/rice2.png" style="max-width: 90%" />
              <br />
            </details>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="content">
            <h1>没玩过原作的 Starfield 同人 OOC 视觉图</h1>

            <h4>标签: 同人 OOC, 屎掘图, 抽象, 抽象艺术, 抽象, (CC 4.0)©</h4>

            <div class="dark">
              <div class="banner color-palette"></div>

              <div class="wallpaper-dark">
                <div class="ion-background"></div>

                <img class="logo-light" src="/images/blogs/starfield/logo.svg" alt="logo" />
              </div>

              <div class="banner color-palette"></div>
            </div>

            <br />

            <div class="light">
              <div class="banner color-palette"></div>

              <div class="wallpaper-light">
                <div class="ion-background"></div>

                <img class="logo" src="/images/blogs/starfield/logo.svg" alt="logo" />
              </div>

              <div class="banner color-palette"></div>
            </div>

            <p>上面👆那两个其实是 CSS 渲染的.</p>
            <p>下面👇是正经图片.</p>

            <div class="preview">
              <img class="preview" src="/images/blogs/starfield/4k-web.png" />
              <br />
              <br />

              <img class="preview" src="/images/blogs/starfield/4k-web-logo.png" />
              <br />
              <br />

              <img class="preview right" src="/images/blogs/starfield/4k-web-logo-dark.png" />

              <br />
              <br />

              <img class="preview" src="/images/blogs/starfield/4k-web-icon.png" />

              <br />
              <br />

              <img class="preview" src="/images/blogs/starfield/4k-web-icon-dark.png" />

              <br />
              <br />

              <img class="preview" src="/images/blogs/starfield/2k-web.png" />

              <br />
              <br />

              <img class="preview" src="/images/blogs/starfield/2k-web-light.png" />
            </div>

            <div class="work">
              <a
                target="_blank"
                href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rainbowflesh/rainbowflesh.github.io/main/images/blogs/starfield/work.psd"
                download="work.psd"
              >
                <button class="btn"> Download 原始檔案 </button>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <BackToTopButton />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .right {
    margin-right: 0;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .preview {
    width: 480px;
  }

  .color-palette {
    --number-of-stripes: 4;
    --stripe-height: 12px;

    background-image: linear-gradient(
      rgb(200, 35, 55) 0%,
      rgb(200, 35, 55) 25%,
      rgb(224, 98, 54) 25%,
      rgb(224, 98, 54) 50%,
      rgb(215, 171, 97) 50%,
      rgb(215, 171, 97) 75%,
      rgb(47, 76, 121) 75%,
      rgb(47, 76, 121) 100%
    );

    height: calc(var(--stripe-height) * var(--number-of-stripes));
  }

  .wallpaper-dark {
    background-image: url("/images/blogs/starfield/gravity_waves.jpg");
    background-size: 100%;
  }

  .wallpaper-light {
    background-image: url("/images/blogs/starfield/gravity_waves_white.jpg");
    background-size: 100%;
  }

  .ion-background {
    background-image: url("/images/blogs/starfield/ION_paper_800px.png");
    overflow-x: clip;
    background-color: rgb(245, 247, 247);
    background-repeat: repeat;
  }

  .logo-light {
    filter: invert(100%);
  }
</style>
